</div>

<!-- ═══════════════ HERO ═══════════════ -->
<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="about-hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="about-hero-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="about-hero-title">MBA · PCC · CPCC · CTCC · Managing Partner</div>
      <h1 class="display-2">Eugene Nkomba</h1>
      <p>Helping leaders build extraordinary businesses while living the life they most want to live — at the intersection of ancient wisdom, neuroscience, and the AI era.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="portrait-block">
      <div class="portrait-frame">
        <img src="eugene-nkomba.jpg" alt="Eugene Nkomba — Executive Coach" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="portrait-accent"></div>
        <div class="portrait-deco"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ BIO ═══════════════ -->
<section class="bio-section">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Credential Badges -->
    <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-bottom:40px;" class="fade-up">
      <span style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:rgba(184,151,90,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(184,151,90,0.25); color:var(--gold-dark); font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.1em; padding:6px 14px; border-radius:100px; text-transform:uppercase;">MBA</span>
      <span style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:rgba(184,151,90,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(184,151,90,0.25); color:var(--gold-dark); font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.1em; padding:6px 14px; border-radius:100px; text-transform:uppercase;">PCC — ICF</span>
      <span style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:rgba(184,151,90,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(184,151,90,0.25); color:var(--gold-dark); font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.1em; padding:6px 14px; border-radius:100px; text-transform:uppercase;">CPCC</span>
      <span style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:rgba(184,151,90,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(184,151,90,0.25); color:var(--gold-dark); font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.1em; padding:6px 14px; border-radius:100px; text-transform:uppercase;">CTCC</span>
    </div>

    <div class="bio-lead fade-up">
      "I coach the WHO, not just the WHAT. Because the greatest leverage point in any organization is the inner maturity of its leaders."
    </div>

    <div class="bio-body">
      <div>
        <p>
          Eugene Nkomba (MBA, PCC, CPCC, CTCC) is an executive coach and the Managing Partner of Maturity Coach — a practice built on a singular conviction: that the quality of a leader's inner life determines the quality of everything their organization produces.
        </p>
        <p>
          With over fifteen years embedded in leadership development, organizational psychology, and neuro-informed coaching, Eugene has guided hundreds of senior leaders across six continents through the most consequential inflection points of their professional lives. His clients include CEOs of growth-stage companies, managing directors at global firms, and founders navigating the complex passage from entrepreneur to enterprise leader.
        </p>
        <p>
          What distinguishes Eugene's work is a rare synthesis: the depth of ancient wisdom traditions — Stoicism, Ubuntu philosophy, Eastern contemplative practice, and the enduring counsel of Proverbs — fused with the precision of modern behavioral neuroscience and a clear-eyed understanding of what it means to lead in an AI-accelerated world.
        </p>
        <p>
          Eugene trained at the Center for Professional Excellence at Concordia University Chicago and holds advanced credentials from the International Coach Federation. He is a sought-after speaker and facilitator, having presented at the Institute of Coaching Boston conference and convened Enterprise Coach Mastery programs for coaches seeking to work at the highest levels of organizational complexity.
        </p>
        <p>
          At the heart of his practice is a provocation that has stopped many a hard-charging executive in their tracks: <em>"AI is making answers faster — but it is not making organizations smarter. That gap is precisely where human maturity lives."</em>
        </p>
        <p>
          Eugene doesn't just coach leaders to perform better. He coaches them to become more fully who they already are — and to discover that this is the source of their most enduring success, and their most enjoyable life.
        </p>

        <div style="margin-top:40px; padding-top:40px; border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
          <div class="section-label">A Personal Word</div>
          <p>
            I grew up understanding that wisdom is not a possession — it is a practice. The elders in my community didn't just know things; they <em>lived</em> things, in ways that made everyone around them better. That understanding has never left me. My work as a coach is, in many ways, a translation of that inheritance into the language of modern organizations.
          </p>
          <p>
            I believe the most powerful thing a leader can do is cultivate the kind of inner stability and expansive self-awareness from which genuinely wise decisions flow. Not because it looks good on paper — but because it produces better outcomes, healthier cultures, and lives that feel, at the end of each day, worth having lived.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="credentials-panel fade-up">
          <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:24px;">Credentials</div>

          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-label">Current Role</div>
            <div class="credential-value">Managing Partner, Maturity Coach</div>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-label">Training</div>
            <div class="credential-value">Center for Professional Excellence, Concordia University Chicago</div>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-label">Certifications</div>
            <div class="credential-value">
              PCC — Professional Certified Coach (ICF)<br>
              CPCC — Certified Professional Co-Active Coach<br>
              CTCC — Certified Team &amp; Culture Coach<br>
              MBA — Master of Business Administration
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-label">Specialization</div>
            <div class="credential-value">AI-Era Leadership · Systems Psychodynamics · Executive Mastery</div>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-label">Experience</div>
            <div class="credential-value">15+ years · 300+ leaders coached</div>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-label">Speaking</div>
            <div class="credential-value">Institute of Coaching, Boston · Enterprise Coach Mastercamp</div>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-label">Original Framework</div>
            <div class="credential-value"><a href="framework.html" style="color:var(--gold); font-weight:500;">The Ubuntu Roots Framework →</a></div>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-label">Connect</div>
            <div class="credential-value">
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nkomba" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:var(--gold); font-weight:500;">LinkedIn Profile →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ VALUES ═══════════════ -->
<section class="values-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center fade-up">
      <div class="section-label" style="justify-content:center; color:var(--gold);">Guiding Principles</div>
      <h2 class="display-3 text-white">What Eugene believes about leadership</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="values-grid" style="margin-top:56px;">
      <div class="value-card fade-up">
        <div class="value-number">01</div>
        <div class="value-title">The WHO precedes the WHAT</div>
        <p class="value-text">Every strategy, decision, and culture flows from the inner state of the leader at the top. Coaching the person — their character, maturity, and self-awareness — is the highest-leverage intervention in any organization.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card fade-up">
        <div class="value-number">02</div>
        <div class="value-title">Enjoyment is not optional</div>
        <p class="value-text">A sustainable high-performance life is not built on sacrifice and willpower — it's built on alignment. When leaders enjoy the life they're living, they lead with more generosity, creativity, and resilience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card fade-up">
        <div class="value-number">03</div>
        <div class="value-title">Ancient wisdom is not old news</div>
        <p class="value-text">The Stoics, the Ubuntu tradition, the wisdom of Proverbs — these are not relics. They are distilled insights from thousands of years of human experience, more relevant than ever in a world of technological acceleration.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card fade-up">
        <div class="value-number">04</div>
        <div class="value-title">Technology amplifies, not replaces</div>
        <p class="value-text">AI is a powerful multiplier — but it multiplies whatever is already there. Mature leaders with strong values and clear self-awareness use AI to go further. Immature leaders use AI to go further in the wrong direction, faster.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ COACHING APPROACH ═══════════════ -->
<section class="approach-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-2" style="align-items:start;">
      <div class="fade-up">
        <div class="section-label">The Approach</div>
        <h2 class="display-3" style="margin-bottom:20px;">How coaching with Eugene works</h2>
        <p class="body-md text-muted">
          Every engagement is tailored — but the movement is always the same. From clarity, to capacity, to mastery.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item fade-up">
            <div class="timeline-dot">🔍</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-title">Deep Inquiry</div>
              <p class="timeline-text">We begin by surfacing what is actually true — not what looks good on paper. A rigorous exploration of your leadership identity, your patterns under pressure, and the life you genuinely want.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item fade-up">
            <div class="timeline-dot">🌱</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-title">Inner Capacity Building</div>
              <p class="timeline-text">Neuroscience-informed practices to strengthen your prefrontal capacity — building the inner stability from which great decisions, honest conversations, and wise leadership naturally emerge.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item fade-up">
            <div class="timeline-dot">⚡</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-title">Strategic Integration</div>
              <p class="timeline-text">Connecting your inner transformation to the real-world challenges on your desk — so every breakthrough in the coaching room translates into tangible results in your business and your life.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item fade-up">
            <div class="timeline-dot">∞</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-title">Sustainable Mastery</div>
              <p class="timeline-text">The goal is not dependency — it's independence. You leave the engagement with new capacities, a clear leadership philosophy, and the self-knowledge to keep growing without a coach by your side.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ CTA ═══════════════ -->
<section class="about-cta">
